Explain difference between JPA and Hibernate:
---------------------------------------------


JPA:- (Java persistence api) :- it is  to develop any ORM based software
JPA - belongs from "javax.persistence" package.




Hibernate:- it is one of the Object Related Mapping based framework software
Hibernate is used for  implementing JPA
Hibernate api comes in the form of "org.hibernate" package.

